== Build Information ==

This build uses the [http://land-boards.com/blwiki/index.php?title=RETRO-EP4CE15 RETRO-EP4CE15], a USB Blaster for the FPGA-chip, the ready-to-use ALTERA-Quartus2 V20.1 software for programming. All c-/asm-source and binary files are included. For assembling/recompiling you need the M80 Assembler and the [https://github.com/douggilliland/Retro-Computers/tree/master/Z80/Software/mescc MESCC C-Compiler system from Github]. Instructions how to do both steps is described in [https://github.com/douggilliland/Retro-Computers/blob/master/Z80/Software/multicomp-z80_xgraph/xgraph.txt 'xgraph.txt'].

